OL,6,FText describing Liz Truss's mini-
OL,7,Fbudget as a "disaster" has been
OL,8,Fremoved from government documents
OL,9,Fafter the former PM complained the
OL,10,Fcivil service had breached
OL,11,Fimpartiality rules.
OL,13,FMs Truss complained that references to
OL,14,Fthe "mistakes" of her economic policy,
OL,15,Fwhich unleashed chaos in the markets,
OL,16,Ftanked the pound and caused mortgage
OL,17,Frates to skyrocket, were "untrue
OL,18,Fpolitical attacks".
